OL,3,CPrime Minister promises to clamp down
OL,4,Con retail crime
OL,6,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak has said
OL,7,Ffresh measures to stop retail crime
OL,8,Fwill show shop workers that "we've got
OL,9,Ftheir back" as he announced assaulting
OL,10,Fshop staff will be made a separate
OL,11,Fcriminal offence.
OL,13,FMr Sunak visited a Boots store in
OL,14,FHorsham, West Sussex, for the
OL,15,Fannouncement where staff showed him
OL,16,Fsafety measures in place for workers,
OL,17,Fsuch as a panic button and bodyworn
OL,18,Fcameras.
