OL,3,CPrime Minister promises to clamp down
OL,4,Con retail crime
OL,6,FSpeaking to reporters at Horsham
OL,7,Fpolice station, he said, "I have been
OL,8,Fconcerned by the rise in retail crime
OL,9,Fas I'm sure many others are either
OL,10,Fseeing it or on social media, which is
OL,11,Fwhy today we've announced a strong set
OL,12,Fof measures to clamp down on retail
OL,13,Fcrime."
OL,15,F"(It's) been warmly welcomed by
OL,16,Fretailers and police that I've spoken
OL,17,Fto today and crucially will
OL,18,Fdemonstrate to our shop workers that
OL,19,Fwe've got their back and also that we
OL,20,Fwill do what it takes to keep our
OL,21,Fstreets and our community safe."
