OL,3,CPrime Minister promises to clamp down
OL,4,Con retail crime
OL,6,FAssaulting a shop worker is to be made
OL,7,Fa separate criminal offence after the
OL,8,FGovernment U-turned in the face of a
OL,9,Flong-running campaign.
OL,11,FMinisters had previously ruled out
OL,12,Flegislating to create a new offence,
OL,13,Fsaying in response to a parliamentary
OL,14,Fpetition in October they did not think
OL,15,Fit was "required or will be most
OL,16,Feffective".
OL,26,@wD@HOUxD@JO]
