OL,3,CPrime Minister promises to clamp down
OL,4,Con retail crime
OL,6,FBut on Wednesday, Mr Sunak announced
OL,7,Fthat his Government will be amending
OL,8,Fits Criminal Justice Bill to bring in
OL,9,Fthe new offence, which will apply to
OL,10,FEngland and Wales.
OL,12,FHe previously said, "I am sending a
OL,13,Fmessage to those criminals ` whether
OL,14,Fthey are serious organised criminal
OL,15,Fgangs, repeat offenders or
OL,16,Fopportunistic thieves ` who think they
OL,17,Fcan get away with stealing from these
OL,18,Flocal businesses or abusing shop
OL,19,Fworkers, enough is enough."
OL,26,@tD@UOU
