OL,3,CPrime Minister promises to clamp down
OL,4,Con retail crime
OL,6,FThe Government also plans to pilot
OL,7,Fcommunity sentencing measures with an
OL,8,Fas yet unnamed police force to tackle
OL,9,Fhigh levels of shoplifting, along with
OL,10,Fgreater use of facial recognition
OL,11,Ftechnology to identify people wanted
OL,12,Fby the police in crowded areas.
OL,14,FJudges already have the power to ban
OL,15,Frepeat offenders from certain shops
OL,16,Funder criminal behaviour orders, with
OL,17,Fbreaches bringing a maximum sentence
OL,18,Fof five years.
