OL,3,CPrime Minister promises to clamp down
OL,4,Con retail crime
OL,6,FThe move to create a separate offence
OL,7,Ffollows a long-running campaign from
OL,8,Fmajor retailers and Conservative
OL,9,Fbackbencher Matt Vickers amid rising
OL,10,Fviolence against retail workers.
OL,12,FOver the past six months, more than
OL,13,F47,000 people have signed a petition
OL,14,Fcalling for the creation of a separate
OL,15,Foffence of assaulting a retail worker.
