OL,6,FShe said, "The impact of retail
OL,7,Fviolence has steadily worsened, with
OL,8,Fpeople facing racial abuse, sexual
OL,9,Fharassment, threatening behaviour,
OL,10,Fphysical assault and threats with
OL,11,Fweapons, often linked to organised
OL,12,Fcrime."
OL,14,F"Victims are ordinary hardworking
OL,15,Fpeople ` teenagers taking on their
OL,16,Ffirst job, carers looking for part-
OL,17,Ftime work, parents working around
OL,18,Fchildcare."
