OL,6,F"I hope that whatever the Government
OL,7,Fis proposing will be substantial and
OL,8,Feffective in giving shop workers, key
OL,9,Fworkers in every community, the
OL,10,Frespect that they have long deserved
OL,11,Fand regrettably too often do not
OL,12,Freceive."
OL,14,FShadow home secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,15,Fsaid the Government's proposals are "a
OL,16,Fpale imitation" of her own party's
