OL,6,FShe said, "Under the Tories, too many
OL,7,Fcommunities and high streets are being
OL,8,Fblighted by staggering increases in
OL,9,Fshoplifting, up 30% in the last year
OL,10,Falone."
OL,12,F"Labour has been calling for tougher
OL,13,Faction against those who assault shop
OL,14,Fworkers for more than 10 years. The
OL,15,FTories opposed and voted against our
OL,16,Fplans for better protection. Why has
OL,17,Fit taken them so long to act?"
